; palette.tres — Endesga 32 palette as a Godot Resource (S-370 §H2.6).
;
; Source: https://lospec.com/palette-list/endesga-32  (CC0, by Endesga)
; 32-color cohesive warm-leaning palette used as the single source of truth
; for every programmatic color in the project. SpriteAtlas, Ground, House,
; Character, BattleLog, HandPicker, PhaseBanner all sample from here via
; client/scripts/globals/Palette.gd.
;
; Indices (0-based):
;   0  #be4a2f  brick red
;   1  #d77643  rust orange
;   2  #ead4aa  cream
;   3  #e4a672  peach (skin highlight)
;   4  #b86f50  tan (skin shadow)
;   5  #733e39  dark brown (hair)
;   6  #3e2731  espresso (outline)
;   7  #a22633  blood red (briefs)
;   8  #e43b44  bright red (briefs hi)
;   9  #f77622  pumpkin
;   10 #feae34  amber
;   11 #fee761  buttercup
;   12 #63c74d  leaf green
;   13 #3e8948  grass green
;   14 #265c42  pine green
;   15 #193c3e  dark teal
;   16 #124e89  navy blue
;   17 #0099db  sky blue
;   18 #2ce8f5  cyan
;   19 #ffffff  white
;   20 #c0cbdc  pale steel
;   21 #8b9bb4  steel blue
;   22 #5a6988  slate
;   23 #3a4466  deep slate
;   24 #262b44  midnight blue
;   25 #181425  obsidian (deep outline)
;   26 #ff0044  pink-red (alarm)
;   27 #68386c  plum
;   28 #b55088  rose pink
;   29 #f6757a  salmon
;   30 #e8b796  shell
;   31 #c28569  brick brown

